(10, 'G6RWI7UJ17773802', 5, '{\"id\":5,\"uniqid\":\"ESD5WZNL17764361\",\"user_id\":4,\"type\":\"{\\\"id\\\":1,\\\"uniqid\\\":\\\"I8GYRA4P17769390\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"WhatsApp Group\\\",\\\"cost\\\":40,\\\"earning\\\":20,\\\"platform\\\":\\\"WhatsApp\\\",\\\"members\\\":100,\\\"status\\\":\\\"active\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2026-04-23 11:11:04\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2026-04-23 11:11:04\\\"}\",\"limit\":56,\"proofs\":0,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.facebookgh.com\\/61575486057076\\/posts\\/pfbid02oEs6PN8kp1xP9Jacq8XgKrHBKmi7S7GpEztv8G9eeZvaJCmcFY4PK76Jkrsyqraxl\\/?mibextid=wwXIfr\",\"caption\":\"\\ud83d\\udea8 WHO IS COLE TOMAS ALLEN?\\r\\n\\r\\nAuthorities have identified the suspect in the White House Correspondents\\u2019 Dinner sh\\u00f8\\u00f8ting as Cole Tomas Allen, a 31-year-old man from Torrance, California, according to law enforcement officials.\\r\\n\\r\\nReports say Allen was arrested after gunf\\u00a1re erupted at the Washington Hilton during the high-profile event attended by President Donald Trump, Vice President J.D. Vance, First Lady Melania Trump, and other top officials.\\r\\n\\r\\nInvestigators believe the suspect may have been a guest at the hotel, though his exact motive has not yet been confirmed.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\ud83d\\udd0e What is known so far:\\r\\n\\u2022 Allen is reportedly a Los Angeles-area resident from Torrance  \\r\\n\\u2022 He is said to be a graduate of the California Institute of Technology (Caltech), earning a degree in mechanical engineering in 2017  \\r\\n\\u2022 A profile linked to his name also claims he later earned a master\\u2019s degree in computer science in 2025  \\r\\n\\u2022 He has worked as a part-time teacher with a tutoring company and also as an independent game developer  \\r\\n\\u2022 Social media and professional profiles describe him as someone involved in science, engineering, and education\\r\\n\\r\\nAccording to officials, the suspect was @rmed with a sh0tg\\u00fcn and opened fire before being quickly subdued by Secret Service agents.\\r\\n\\r\\nOne law enforcement officer was injured but survived thanks to protective gear. All senior officials, including the President and Vice President, were safely evacuated.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u26a0\\ufe0f Authorities say investigations are still ongoing, and no confirmed motive has been released.\\r\\n\\r\\nThis remains a developing story.\",\"banner\":\"1777231006.jpeg\",\"status\":\"active\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-26 20:17:41\",\"date\":\"2026-04-17 15:29:38\"}', '{\"Screenshot\":\" <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/172.20.10.5\\/wenorgigs\\/public\\/tasks\\/proofs\\/kn7qxayg17773802.png\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" class=\\\"c-primary no-select w-fit\\\">\\n                        View Screenshot\\n                        <svg xmlns=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.w3.org\\/2000\\/svg\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 256 256\\\" fill=\\\"CurrentColor\\\" height=\\\"15\\\" width=\\\"15\\\"><path d=\\\"M228,104a12,12,0,0,1-24,0V69l-59.51,59.51a12,12,0,0,1-17-17L187,52H152a12,12,0,0,1,0-24h64a12,12,0,0,1,12,12Zm-44,24a12,12,0,0,0-12,12v64H52V84h64a12,12,0,0,0,0-24H48A20,20,0,0,0,28,80V208a20,20,0,0,0,20,20H176a20,20,0,0,0,20-20V140A12,12,0,0,0,184,128Z\\\"><\\/path><\\/svg>\\n\\n                    <\\/a>\"}', NULL, 'approved', '2026-04-28 20:45:02', '2026-04-28 20:44:53'),
